{"tid":2239553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Lunch哥向謝振中投訴濫捕","createTime":"2020-10-12T04:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T04:34:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce54e3605004bca9570994693e8253c20fb648e4","tid":2239553,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/J5GKUBHC2NABNJLX5VRGPA656A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FJ5GKUBHC2NABNJLX5VRGPA656A%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=07009687\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FJ5GKUBHC2NABNJLX5VRGPA656A%2F&h=21f1431d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/J5GKUBHC2NABNJLX5VRGPA656A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nLunch哥向謝振中投訴濫捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qbQ2LVwiH2xvuPWgXCAaMG3-1Cw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OGWI7F2NGJHBBFMJZRYHJJAU7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqbQ2LVwiH2xvuPWgXCAaMG3-1Cw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOGWI7F2NGJHBBFMJZRYHJJAU7A.jpg&h=f3333131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「Lunch哥」David昨晚前往青衣警署遞交請願信（圖），投訴警方上周在青衣城無理拘捕。他預計信件未必有實際效用，但認為不能因此拒絕發聲。傳媒採訪時三名警員稱收到報案，指有多於四人聚集，警告記者須立即分散，並要求出示記者證及身份證，惟其後又改稱只須檢查記者證。其中一名警員質疑立場新聞記者證件上沒編號，逐一抄下記者代表的傳媒機構後返署，未有進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\nDavid在本月4日在青衣城舉行「青衣和你睇《蘋果》」，警方截查後將他帶到青衣警署，聲稱協助調查，其後指他「引嚟好多記者，破壞社會安寧」，以公眾地方行為不檢罪名拘捕他。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥警公報私仇<br />\n<br />\nDavid形容拘捕理由荒謬，警員不友善反映自己被針對，批評警方濫捕、公報私仇，故到警署遞信投訴。信函要求葵青區指揮官謝振中盡快了解、對相關警員作處分、撤銷檢控及安排會面等。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「將個責任交返畀警方，係警察唔查，唔係我唔投訴。」"},{"pid":"8f2581819d0795eb6c9ffe6fe369be275234b20f","tid":2239553,"uid":57488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"想問下寫俾謝振中做乜柒"},{"pid":"3e205bd9edebc9e86442eedeafa7d643b0bab77c","tid":2239553,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:34:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}